<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
   <style>
              .email{
                         width: 100%;
                     }
                     .top{
                         width: 1000px;
                         margin-left: auto;
                         margin-right: auto;
                          margin-bottom: 20px;
                     }
                     .top  img {
                         width: 100%;
                     }
                     .fater{
                         width: 1000px;
                         margin-left: auto;
                         margin-right: auto;
                         background: whitesmoke;
                     }
                     .fater  .img-qr {
                         width: 126px;
                         margin-left: auto;
                         margin-right: auto;
                         text-align: center;
                     }
                     .fater  .img-qr  img{
                         width:100%;
                         margin-left: auto;
                         margin-right: auto;
                         margin-top: 15px;
                     }
                     .fater  .text {
                         margin-top: 25px;
                         text-align: center;
                         margin-left: auto;
                         margin-right: auto;
                     }
                     .fater  .text  p {
                         margin-left: auto;
                         margin-right: auto;
                         width:345px;
                         color:#666666;
                         word-wrap:break-word;
                         word-break:break-all;
                     }
                     .center {
                         width: 1000px;
                         margin-left: auto;
                         margin-right: auto;
                         margin-bottom:20px;
                         font-size: 16px;
                         color:#333333;
                     }
                     .center .box{
                             width: 800px;
                              margin-left: auto;
                              margin-right: auto;

                     }
                     .box  p {
                        text-indent:2em;
                     }
                     .center .text{
                         margin-top: 10px;
                         color:black;
                         text-indent:2em;
                     }
                     .center .buttom{
                         margin-top: 10px;
                     }
     </style>
<body>
<div class="email">
<div class="top">
     <img src="https://huluwa-pdf.oss-cn-qingdao.aliyuncs.com/email_img/nav.png" alt=""/>

</div>
   <div class="center">
     <div class="box">
   ${content}

    </div>
   </div>
 <div class="fater">
     <div class="img-qr">
         <img src="https://huluwa-pdf.oss-cn-qingdao.aliyuncs.com/email_img/qr.png" alt=""/>
     </div>
     <div class="text">
         <p>
             扫码关注放心签公众号，随时掌握放心签动态，了解更多电子合同相关知识
         </p>
     </div>

 </div>
 </div>
</body>  
</html>
